properties.areaDesc: Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 20 at 4:09AM AKST until February 21 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Fairbanks, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow and blowing snow occurring. Visibility one half mile
or less at times. Less than 1 inch of additional snow
accumulation expected. Travel will be difficult.

* WHERE...Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM Friday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...North winds gusting to 40 mph will cause
low visibility in blowing snow. Significant drifting snow will
occur. Conditions are much less severe at Unalakleet.
properties.instruction:
A Winter Weather Advisory for snow means periods of snow will
cause travel difficulties.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM AKST FRIDAY
